<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.8.10">
<l>uṭampiṉāṟ kuṟaivillā vuyirpirinta malaittuṇṭaṅ</l>
<l>kiṭantaṉapō ṟuṇipalavā vacurarkuḻān tuṇittukanta</l>
<l>taṭampuṉala caṭaimuṭiyaṉ ṟaṉiyorukū ṟamarntuṟaiyu</l>
<l>muṭampuṭaiyāṉ kavarāta vuyiriṉāṟ kuṟaivilamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>uṭampiṉāṉ kuṟaiv* illā ~uyir pirinta malai+ tuṇṭam</l>
<l>kiṭantaṉa pōl tuṇi pala ~ā ~acurar kuḻām tuṇitt* ukanta</l>
<l>taṭam puṉala caṭai muṭiyaṉ taṉi ~oru kūṟ* amarnt* uṟaiyum</l>
<l>uṭamp* uṭaiyāṉ kavarāta ~uyiriṉāṉ kuṟaiv* ilam-ē.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
